# Copy to .dev.vars for local development (never commit .dev.vars).
# ENVIRONMENT=development enables the dev-only X-Forwarded-Host override in
# src/middleware/guard.ts (wrangler dev rewrites the Host header, making
# subdomains untestable otherwise). The committed wrangler.jsonc ships
# ENVIRONMENT=production, so deploys fail closed.
ENVIRONMENT="development"
# Turnstile "always passes" test secret key — replace with the real secret in prod
# via `wrangler secret put TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY`.
TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY="1x0000000000000000000000000000000AA"
# OPTIONAL: enable the /admin blocklist surface locally by uncommenting and
# setting your own key (hex pubkey or npub1…). Leave commented for the default
# fail-closed state — scripts/smoke.sh asserts /admin 404s when unset.
# ADMIN_PUBKEY="npub1..."
